result.execSummary:
The defendant was charged with both OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) .133 and Operating w/ PAC (4th w/in 5 yrs). The defendant was found guilty of OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) .133 and the other charge, Operating w/ PAC (4th w/in 5 yrs) was dismissed by the court.

  • Frank J. Dalka IV was found guilty of OWI (4th w/in 5 yrs) .133, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(1)(a).
